channel.title: Using kiss to make an Alan walker lead
channel.description: So with the new update I’ve been getting back into auxy, and I figured out something neat. Using kiss I was able to make a lead that sounds like the lead from Fade. Take a listen - https://app.auxy.co/projects/x8AuJTfkKRiMSiCjZdkf-A== Feel free to use it as a preset if you want
